User: Look up the CEO of OpenAI -> {"intent":"web_search","model":"remote/kimi-k2-6","tools":["web_search"]}
User: Look up how to fix this Python error online -> {"intent":"web_search","model":"remote/kimi-k2-6","tools":["web_search"]}
